{"word":"G2767 - κεράννυμι - keránnymi - ker-an'-noo-mee - Fill","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κεράννυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">keránnymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ker-an'-noo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fill</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கலந்திரு, கலந்துகொடு"},{"paragraph":"to mix, mingle"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of a more primary word <b>&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>kerao&#x0304;</b> (which is used in certain tenses); to <i>mingle</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>pour</i> out (for drinking): - fill, pour out. Compare <a href=\"#/G3396 - μίγνυμι - mígnymi - mig'-noo-mee/3396\">G3396</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}